data.value: Concorde El Salam Hotel Cairo, located 25 minutes from the city center, offers elegant rooms with balconies overlooking gardens or pools, free Wi-Fi, and flat-screen TVs. The hotel features 8 dining options, 2 outdoor pools, and live entertainment at La Veranda. Amenities include a spa, gym, squash court, and equestrian center. It’s a 10-minute drive from Cairo Airport and offers an airport shuttle.
